# Geometry

## Spacing

To ensure consistent spacing across the app, use these geometry variables whenever possible. 

``` plain
$spacing-large: 38px;
$spacing-medium: 22px;
$spacing-small: 10px;

```

To follow best practice, create a new semantic variable for each component that then references the geometry variables:

``` plain
$paragraph-padding: 0 0 $spacing-medium 0;

p {
  padding: $paragraph-padding;
}

```
